		{
			dependencies: ["D013"]
			description: [
				"The §eController§r is the beating heart of every Refined Storage network. Every cable and component must trace a path back to the Controller to function."
				""
				"§7Requirements:§r"
				"- Requires a continuous supply of §eFE§r (Forge Energy) to stay active"
				"- Without power the entire network goes offline"
				"- One Controller per subnet (subnets can be linked via Network Cards)"
				""
				"Place the Controller, connect it to a power source, and it will glow — your network is forming!"
